1
00:01:03,020 --> 00:01:07,770
[A Prime Minister's Disguise]

2
00:01:08,380 --> 00:01:10,730
[Episode 4]

3
00:01:12,410 --> 00:01:14,590
Why don't you go take a rest first?

4
00:01:14,730 --> 00:01:16,100
When Miss Ling'er comes out,

5
00:01:16,100 --> 00:01:17,630
I'll tell you immediately.

6
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:18,840
I'll just take a look.

7
00:01:19,490 --> 00:01:20,920
This woman is too fierce.

8
00:01:21,230 --> 00:01:22,430
Don't let her escape.

9
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:25,890
Commander ordered us
to keep an eye on her.

10
00:01:26,150 --> 00:01:27,410
She can't go anywhere.

11
00:01:28,039 --> 00:01:29,120
But you...

12
00:01:30,070 --> 00:01:31,080
can leave now.

13
00:01:32,530 --> 00:01:33,930
Attitude!

14
00:01:34,009 --> 00:01:35,500
You pulled me just now.

15
00:01:35,530 --> 00:01:36,720
Don't you remember who provides you

16
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:37,940
with food and shelter?

17
00:01:37,940 --> 00:01:39,789
If you don't provide me
with food or shelter,

18
00:01:39,789 --> 00:01:41,070
in this mansion,

19
00:01:41,070 --> 00:01:43,680
who else can stand up to that one inside?

20
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,680
Yunqing,

21
00:01:46,150 --> 00:01:47,110
Think about it.

22
00:01:47,150 --> 00:01:48,050
If my brother

23
00:01:48,070 --> 00:01:49,930
can live a good life in the palace,

24
00:01:49,970 --> 00:01:51,850
it'd be a good thing for me.

25
00:01:53,770 --> 00:01:54,890
Alright.

26
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,560
It's almost time for dinner.

27
00:01:57,580 --> 00:01:59,270
The dishes here are amazing.

28
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,760
Let's have something delicious first.

29
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:02,160
Pick the expensive ones.

30
00:02:02,790 --> 00:02:03,790
Five Delicacies?

31
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:06,060
Hundred Birds Court the Phoenix?

32
00:02:12,910 --> 00:02:15,070
Ling'er must be hiding something from me.

33
00:02:15,070 --> 00:02:16,020
Could it be...

34
00:02:18,660 --> 00:02:21,880
[Memorial]

35
00:02:22,079 --> 00:02:23,630
A servant of the Minister of Rites

36
00:02:23,630 --> 00:02:26,150
hit a stableman
of the Vice Minister of Revenue?

37
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:29,150
A leaking roof
at the Imperial College needs repairs?

38
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:32,200
The memorials from civil officials
are so boring.

39
00:02:35,630 --> 00:02:36,710
Vassal kings?

40
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:44,470
How come quite a few memorials

41
00:02:44,470 --> 00:02:46,130
have mentioned vassal kings?

42
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:48,800
The vassal kings expanded armies

43
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,490
and hiked taxes without permission.

44
00:02:50,490 --> 00:02:51,190
[Report]

45
00:02:51,190 --> 00:02:52,579
Looks like someone has arranged

46
00:02:52,579 --> 00:02:54,290
court officials to submit these memorials.

47
00:02:54,290 --> 00:02:56,210
Could it be Huo Jingheng?

48
00:02:56,590 --> 00:02:57,720
Could it be...

49
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,630
he's trying to remove their titles?

50
00:02:59,630 --> 00:03:01,090
Interesting.

51
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:02,380
I need to go take a look.

52
00:03:02,910 --> 00:03:03,560
Yue,

53
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:04,840
I'm going to take a nap.

54
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:07,040
Don't let anyone come in and disturb me.

55
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:10,120
This is outrageous!

56
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:13,240
How dare vassal kings
hike taxes without permission,

57
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,970
exploiting the common people!

58
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:17,950
He's so angry.

59
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,680
Huo Jingheng usually

60
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:21,740
doesn't show his emotions so easily.

61
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:24,910
I believe the welfare of the people
should be our priority now.

62
00:03:24,910 --> 00:03:27,520
We must urge the vassal kings
to reduce their military forces,

63
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:28,680
return land to the people,

64
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:31,240
and restore peace to their lives.

65
00:03:31,310 --> 00:03:32,600
Minister Du has a point.

66
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:34,110
I second this proposal.

67
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:36,280
I disagree.

68
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:38,760
Your Majesty,

69
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:41,240
if we insist on
reducing the military forces,

70
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:43,030
how can the vassal kings

71
00:03:43,079 --> 00:03:45,750
defend their own territories?

72
00:03:45,890 --> 00:03:47,450
Lord Ouyang, what do you mean

73
00:03:47,450 --> 00:03:49,340
by "their own territories"?

74
00:03:49,370 --> 00:03:52,270
There's only Ning, and Ning alone.

75
00:03:52,300 --> 00:03:53,620
Ning's territories

76
00:03:53,650 --> 00:03:56,020
should be protected by Ning's armies.

77
00:03:56,050 --> 00:03:58,050
Prime Minister, are you suggesting

78
00:03:58,700 --> 00:04:00,210
vassal kings' armies

79
00:04:00,300 --> 00:04:02,660
don't belong to Ning?

80
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:04,190
Prime Minister, don't forget

81
00:04:04,190 --> 00:04:05,780
Ning was established

82
00:04:05,810 --> 00:04:07,340
by His Majesty

83
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:09,480
and the vassal kings together.

84
00:04:09,510 --> 00:04:11,510
Are you accusing His Majesty

85
00:04:11,530 --> 00:04:14,090
of forgetting the brotherhood

86
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:16,149
and attempting to weaken the vassal kings?

87
00:04:16,149 --> 00:04:17,120
Yes, Your Majesty.

88
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,560
If the vassal kings heard it,

89
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:20,750
it would surely hurt the feelings of them

90
00:04:20,750 --> 00:04:22,360
and cause unrest.

91
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:23,920
Currently, we face

92
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:25,190
both internal and external problems.

93
00:04:25,190 --> 00:04:26,990
We can't curtail their power easily.

94
00:04:26,990 --> 00:04:27,680
Enough!

95
00:04:30,750 --> 00:04:32,210
We will discuss the matter

96
00:04:32,950 --> 00:04:34,110
of the vassal kings later.

97
00:04:34,110 --> 00:04:36,790
Looks like Huo Jingheng wants
to curtail the vassal kings' power.

98
00:04:36,790 --> 00:04:39,070
So he deliberately
put on act with Du Tianzhao

99
00:04:39,070 --> 00:04:41,190
to test the court officials' attitude.

100
00:04:41,190 --> 00:04:42,730
Huo Jingheng

101
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,860
actually has some grasp of statecraft.

102
00:04:44,860 --> 00:04:46,190
Why didn't you just propose

103
00:04:46,190 --> 00:04:47,550
removing the vassal kings' titles?

104
00:04:47,550 --> 00:04:48,370
Now look what happened.

105
00:04:48,370 --> 00:04:49,890
Ouyang Wen gained the upper hand.

106
00:04:49,890 --> 00:04:52,350
The court's opinion has completely tilted.

107
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:54,470
It's not proper
to bring up the matter again.

108
00:04:54,470 --> 00:04:56,900
I just wanted to test

109
00:04:56,930 --> 00:04:58,720
the court officials' attitude.

110
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:01,360
The vassal kings
are growing more arrogant,

111
00:05:01,380 --> 00:05:02,980
but you seem quite composed.

112
00:05:03,050 --> 00:05:04,190
Do you know

113
00:05:04,340 --> 00:05:06,940
how many soldiers the vassal kings have?

114
00:05:07,420 --> 00:05:09,280
Merely over 500,000 soldiers, right?

115
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:12,010
Man King alone
has over 400,000 elite soldiers.

116
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:13,310
Over 400,000?

117
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:16,450
Ning's court only has 600,000 soldiers.

118
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,190
If we push the vassal kings too hard,

119
00:05:18,190 --> 00:05:19,530
and they all rebel against us,

120
00:05:19,530 --> 00:05:21,150
with those soldiers we have,

121
00:05:22,100 --> 00:05:24,160
I'm afraid we won't hold out for long.

122
00:05:24,430 --> 00:05:26,000
Given the current situation,

123
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:28,010
it's best to take no action.

124
00:05:28,100 --> 00:05:30,510
Then why did you discuss it

125
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,710
with the court officials?

126
00:05:31,710 --> 00:05:33,590
The vassal kings have

127
00:05:33,830 --> 00:05:35,340
their own spies in the court,

128
00:05:35,340 --> 00:05:36,830
all bribed.

129
00:05:37,190 --> 00:05:39,870
I just wanted to warn the vassal kings

130
00:05:40,060 --> 00:05:41,740
through them.

131
00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:45,580
As for

132
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:48,480
how to resolve this,

133
00:05:50,909 --> 00:05:53,510
I still don't have a proper solution.

134
00:05:53,740 --> 00:05:54,900
But Uncle,

135
00:05:55,390 --> 00:05:58,010
I saw the memorials
you submitted a few days ago.

136
00:05:58,010 --> 00:06:00,080
Everything was handled properly.

137
00:06:00,190 --> 00:06:02,480
And there were lots of good ideas.

138
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,000
But on this matter

139
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:06,360
of removing the vassal kings' titles,

140
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:08,260
why are you so hesitant?

141
00:06:08,430 --> 00:06:11,600
You're giving me a warning now.

142
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:13,000
So you've caught on to it?

143
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:15,680
I heard

144
00:06:15,740 --> 00:06:18,820
you recently took in a distant relative.

145
00:06:18,850 --> 00:06:20,270
There must be many things to handle.

146
00:06:20,270 --> 00:06:23,440
I guess that is
what has been distracting you.

147
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,060
How about this?

148
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:31,230
I'll allow you to return home

149
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:33,159
to take care of your family affairs.

150
00:06:33,159 --> 00:06:34,360
And rest for a few days.

151
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,070
Don't.

152
00:06:35,110 --> 00:06:35,920
My dear nephew,

153
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:36,740
I don't need to rest.

154
00:06:36,740 --> 00:06:37,720
I can handle it.

155
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:39,290
Then I'll dock your salary.

156
00:06:39,460 --> 00:06:40,470
Rest as long as you like.

157
00:06:40,470 --> 00:06:41,800
For each day off, you lose pay.

158
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,790
Fair and just.

159
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:43,800
No, no, no.

160
00:06:43,870 --> 00:06:45,430
Don't dock my salary.

161
00:06:45,430 --> 00:06:45,950
If you dock my salary,

162
00:06:45,950 --> 00:06:47,159
how am I supposed to live?

163
00:06:47,159 --> 00:06:48,390
I have a large family to support!

164
00:06:48,390 --> 00:06:50,240
Then how to solve the vassal kings' issue?

165
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:50,920
Give me

166
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,070
a solution right now.

167
00:06:52,070 --> 00:06:52,630
I...

168
00:06:53,430 --> 00:06:54,070
Wei Zhang,

169
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:54,720
go.

170
00:06:54,750 --> 00:06:55,950
Ask for a leave on behalf of him.

171
00:06:55,950 --> 00:06:56,490
Yes.

172
00:06:56,630 --> 00:06:57,240
No!

173
00:06:57,610 --> 00:06:59,500
I beg your forgiveness, Your Majesty!

174
00:06:59,500 --> 00:07:01,270
Those memorials...

175
00:07:02,070 --> 00:07:03,600
were not reviewed by me.

176
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:05,820
Really?

177
00:07:07,190 --> 00:07:08,270
By whom then?

178
00:07:10,830 --> 00:07:11,950
By...

179
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:14,320
Just keep your mouth shut.

180
00:07:18,390 --> 00:07:20,110
By Consort Yue.

181
00:07:23,860 --> 00:07:24,990
Consort Yue?

182
00:07:25,890 --> 00:07:26,690
Uncle,

183
00:07:26,870 --> 00:07:28,870
even if you don't have a solution
for the vassal kings' issue,

184
00:07:28,870 --> 00:07:30,540
I won't blame you.

185
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:32,380
Why did you come up with

186
00:07:32,400 --> 00:07:33,980
such a ridiculous excuse to deceive me?

187
00:07:33,980 --> 00:07:35,710
I wouldn't dare, Your Majesty.

188
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,690
Well, since

189
00:07:36,710 --> 00:07:38,940
you're so certain,

190
00:07:39,710 --> 00:07:40,570
let's

191
00:07:41,130 --> 00:07:42,530
go to the Fengluan Palace

192
00:07:42,650 --> 00:07:44,780
and confront Consort Yue face to face.

193
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:52,100
Welcome, Your Majesty.

194
00:07:59,390 --> 00:08:00,480
Yue, serve tea.

195
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,190
No need.

196
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,450
She is kneeling at the door.

197
00:08:03,750 --> 00:08:04,730
Consort Yue,

198
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:08,600
I heard although you're in the harem,

199
00:08:08,810 --> 00:08:10,470
you care about court affairs.

200
00:08:12,410 --> 00:08:14,140
I wouldn't dare, Your Majesty.

201
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,190
I just heard Lord Du

202
00:08:16,220 --> 00:08:18,880
complaining about trivial court affairs,

203
00:08:19,010 --> 00:08:20,520
so I spoke out of turn.

204
00:08:20,820 --> 00:08:22,760
I shouldn't have discussed state affairs.

205
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:24,490
Your Majesty, please punish me.

206
00:08:24,490 --> 00:08:25,790
So,

207
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:28,720
Minister Du

208
00:08:28,930 --> 00:08:31,850
met privately with my Consort Yue?

209
00:08:33,169 --> 00:08:34,690
I swear to God!

210
00:08:34,750 --> 00:08:35,549
Your Majesty,

211
00:08:35,650 --> 00:08:37,590
there's nothing
between Consort Yue and me.

212
00:08:37,590 --> 00:08:39,230
A few days ago,

213
00:08:39,250 --> 00:08:40,830
when I passed the Shoukang Palace,

214
00:08:40,830 --> 00:08:42,120
I ran into Consort Yue.

215
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:44,400
I'm an old acquaintance of the Yue family,

216
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:46,460
so we exchanged a few words.

217
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:48,820
You exchanged a few words,

218
00:08:48,950 --> 00:08:51,010
and she helped you review memorials?

219
00:08:54,860 --> 00:08:55,670
Lord Du,

220
00:08:56,430 --> 00:08:58,290
let's be honest with His Majesty.

221
00:08:58,750 --> 00:08:59,810
Tell him the truth.

222
00:09:03,870 --> 00:09:04,750
Your Majesty,

223
00:09:05,430 --> 00:09:06,470
a few days ago,

224
00:09:06,640 --> 00:09:08,220
Lord Du came to me,

225
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:10,660
asking me
to secretly review memorials for him.

226
00:09:10,660 --> 00:09:12,320
I certainly didn't have the guts.

227
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:14,080
But I didn't expect Lord Du...

228
00:09:16,910 --> 00:09:19,120
to threaten me.

229
00:09:19,150 --> 00:09:20,920
Consort Yue, watch your mouth.

230
00:09:20,950 --> 00:09:22,880
Think about the entire Yue family.

231
00:09:23,580 --> 00:09:24,850
Your Majesty, look.

232
00:09:25,180 --> 00:09:27,550
That is exactly how he threatened me.

233
00:09:27,980 --> 00:09:29,160
So,

234
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,820
it's Minister Du's fault?

235
00:09:32,140 --> 00:09:33,010
Minister Du,

236
00:09:33,030 --> 00:09:34,450
how should we handle this matter?

237
00:09:34,450 --> 00:09:35,760
I'm afraid

238
00:09:35,780 --> 00:09:38,180
a mere salary cut
can't silence the rumors.

239
00:09:40,310 --> 00:09:42,400
What rumors?

240
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,510
I admit my guilt.

241
00:09:45,590 --> 00:09:49,260
I've known Consort Yue and Yue Chi
since childhood.

242
00:09:49,390 --> 00:09:52,240
I'm well aware that Consort Yue

243
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:54,390
has been influenced by Yue Chi's insights.

244
00:09:54,390 --> 00:09:55,520
She's resourceful.

245
00:09:55,570 --> 00:09:58,060
I was truly overwhelmed

246
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,720
by the court affairs.

247
00:09:59,740 --> 00:10:01,860
So I asked for Consort Yue's help.

248
00:10:03,310 --> 00:10:04,290
I didn't know

249
00:10:04,870 --> 00:10:07,330
Consort Yue has such great talent.

250
00:10:07,710 --> 00:10:09,910
How can I let such a pearl remain hidden?

251
00:10:10,140 --> 00:10:13,220
I'm not narrow-minded.

252
00:10:13,250 --> 00:10:16,800
I want to remove the vassal kings' titles.

253
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:17,860
Consort Yue,

254
00:10:17,860 --> 00:10:20,320
are you willing to help me?

255
00:10:23,270 --> 00:10:25,220
I am just a woman.

256
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:27,200
I know nothing of such matters.

257
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,750
Minister Du, you said something

258
00:10:28,750 --> 00:10:30,550
about the Yue family just now?

259
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:32,710
The Yue family...

260
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:35,910
Consort Yue, don't be afraid.

261
00:10:35,910 --> 00:10:38,500
I won't make you do that.

262
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,670
If you truly are unwilling,

263
00:10:40,690 --> 00:10:42,290
I won't force you.

264
00:10:45,930 --> 00:10:47,350
I am willing.

265
00:10:48,010 --> 00:10:50,410
Truly, without the slightest reluctance.

266
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,800
[Yongqian Palace]

267
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:57,440
Wait.

268
00:10:57,860 --> 00:11:00,030
From the moment I returned to the capital,

269
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:00,690
was all this

270
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,270
a trap you set for me?

271
00:11:02,290 --> 00:11:04,640
When did you become so clever?

272
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:07,120
Nephew, are you playing me?

273
00:11:07,170 --> 00:11:08,440
You're not happy?

274
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:11,390
You live a life of luxury every day.

275
00:11:11,470 --> 00:11:12,510
It's only right

276
00:11:12,550 --> 00:11:15,600
to do something for Ning.

277
00:11:15,900 --> 00:11:18,080
Otherwise, I might send you

278
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:20,510
to serve the empress dowager someday.

279
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,150
You're right.

280
00:11:24,510 --> 00:11:25,720
I'll keep it in mind.

281
00:11:26,330 --> 00:11:27,330
It's my pleasure.

282
00:11:28,210 --> 00:11:29,730
I really can't afford

283
00:11:30,190 --> 00:11:31,780
to offend either of them.

284
00:11:33,160 --> 00:11:34,260
Wait a minute.

285
00:11:34,280 --> 00:11:35,670
He went to such lengths

286
00:11:35,670 --> 00:11:37,200
for Consort Yue.

287
00:11:37,220 --> 00:11:37,960
Could it be that he knows

288
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:39,320
that guy is Yue Chi?

289
00:11:41,470 --> 00:11:44,090
When did you start planning that?

290
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:44,860
Was...

291
00:11:44,880 --> 00:11:48,010
Consort Yue's entry to the palace
also part of your plan?

292
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:50,270
Yes.

293
00:11:50,820 --> 00:11:53,900
From the day I summoned her to the palace,

294
00:11:54,930 --> 00:11:56,590
every move was part of my plan.

295
00:11:56,940 --> 00:11:59,180
Why do you value Consort Yue so much?

296
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,260
First,

297
00:12:00,390 --> 00:12:03,040
Consort Yue was always by Yue Chi's side.

298
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:05,900
Second, after Yue Chi's death,

299
00:12:06,030 --> 00:12:07,790
