301
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:12,240
but Ning is still plagued
by internal and external threats.

302
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:14,500
If I could gain the Qilin Army's loyalty,

303
00:12:15,180 --> 00:12:18,240
the world could gain more peace.

304
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:22,870
That's it?

305
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:24,150
That's it.

306
00:12:25,510 --> 00:12:26,790
It seems he

307
00:12:26,870 --> 00:12:29,200
doesn't know his favored consort is a man.

308
00:12:29,630 --> 00:12:31,650
His eyesight is truly terrible.

309
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,550
But that's a good thing too.

310
00:12:33,550 --> 00:12:35,080
As long as Yue Chi and he

311
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,260
can get along well

312
00:12:36,550 --> 00:12:39,200
and be good partners,

313
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:42,240
Ling'er won't have to be his consort.

314
00:12:44,210 --> 00:12:45,600
Very good.

315
00:12:45,740 --> 00:12:47,750
I'll do my best to help you.

316
00:12:48,670 --> 00:12:50,200
Thank you, Uncle.

317
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:06,670
Tianzhao?

318
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:12,400
Did something happen to my brother?

319
00:13:14,510 --> 00:13:16,800
Your brother reviewed memorials for me.

320
00:13:16,870 --> 00:13:18,190
His Majesty found out.

321
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:20,940
But don't worry.

322
00:13:21,140 --> 00:13:22,740
Instead of blaming him,

323
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:24,150
His Majesty praised him.

324
00:13:24,150 --> 00:13:26,750
He asked for his advice
on tough state affairs.

325
00:13:28,320 --> 00:13:29,440
That's great.

326
00:13:30,910 --> 00:13:32,550
It's all thanks to you.

327
00:13:32,870 --> 00:13:33,630
Otherwise,

328
00:13:33,670 --> 00:13:35,870
who knows how long we'd have had to wait?

329
00:13:36,750 --> 00:13:37,440
But...

330
00:13:37,670 --> 00:13:39,910
you're this happy about it?

331
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,200
Of course I'm happy.

332
00:13:42,550 --> 00:13:43,440
That means

333
00:13:43,670 --> 00:13:45,000
Consort Yue is in favor.

334
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:47,520
It's a good thing for me.

335
00:13:47,670 --> 00:13:48,440
Right,

336
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,570
Yunqing

337
00:13:49,590 --> 00:13:51,260
hasn't had much of an appetite lately.

338
00:13:51,260 --> 00:13:53,260
She really should try this.

339
00:13:54,870 --> 00:13:55,580
Thanks.

340
00:14:00,970 --> 00:14:01,520
Ling'er!

341
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,500
Commander ordered me to protect her.

342
00:14:04,500 --> 00:14:05,870
Outsiders can't get close to her.

343
00:14:05,870 --> 00:14:07,120
I'm not an outsider.

344
00:14:07,270 --> 00:14:08,150
Commander said

345
00:14:08,170 --> 00:14:09,880
I should be especially wary of you.

346
00:14:09,880 --> 00:14:11,220
Your room is over there.

347
00:14:11,810 --> 00:14:12,690
Please go back.

348
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:16,640
Sir.

349
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,200
I received news from the palace.

350
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,620
Consort Yue has come up with an idea.

351
00:14:21,620 --> 00:14:23,160
They want you to discuss it
in the palace tomorrow.

352
00:14:23,160 --> 00:14:24,040
So fast?

353
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:25,740
That's great!

354
00:14:26,900 --> 00:14:28,780
Selecting heirs of vassal kings?

355
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:29,390
Yes.

356
00:14:29,880 --> 00:14:31,930
