to the legitimate eldest son.

360
00:14:37,690 --> 00:14:39,550
You only need to issue an edict,

361
00:14:39,580 --> 00:14:42,610
allowing all sons, legitimate or not,

362
00:14:42,640 --> 00:14:43,680
