373
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:05,200
we can divide the inheritance

374
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:06,670
among multiple heirs?

375
00:15:06,910 --> 00:15:07,480
Correct.

376
00:15:07,750 --> 00:15:09,270
And how do we select them?

377
00:15:09,290 --> 00:15:10,980
Establish an academy in the capital

378
00:15:10,980 --> 00:15:12,610
to educate the sons of the vassal kings.

379
00:15:12,610 --> 00:15:14,610
Then we select heirs among them.

380
00:15:15,270 --> 00:15:16,080
In this way,

381
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:18,280
to compete for territories, their sons

382
00:15:18,360 --> 00:15:20,480
