439
00:17:08,089 --> 00:17:09,540
You don't need another.

440
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:11,150
That's true.

441
00:17:12,920 --> 00:17:14,400
When it comes to practical matters,

442
00:17:14,400 --> 00:17:16,109
