444
00:17:18,700 --> 00:17:20,630
Consort Yue, you're far-sighted.

445
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:25,010
Then... I'll ask Minister Du to help you.

446
00:17:25,890 --> 00:17:26,579
I...

447
