00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:02,880
I absolutely believe that there's nothing

465
00:18:02,880 --> 00:18:04,640
between you two.

466
00:18:05,650 --> 00:18:06,350
Here.

467
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:07,700
It's settled.

468
00:18:08,040 --> 00:18:08,530
Take it.

469
00:18:08,530 --> 00:18:09,370
[Token]

470
00:18:11,760 --> 00:18:12,350
