512
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:02,310
Since you've already decided,

513
00:20:02,350 --> 00:20:04,030
we'll proceed accordingly.

514
00:20:04,270 --> 00:20:06,060
If someone else had said that,

515
00:20:06,700 --> 00:20:08,150
I wouldn't ask further.

516
00:20:08,550 --> 00:20:10,970
But the idea to curb the vassal kings

517
00:20:11,450 --> 00:20:12,970
came from you.

518
00:20:13,750 --> 00:20:15,420
So your opinion matters more.

519
00:20:15,470 --> 00:20:16,370
Okay.

520
00:20:16,660 --> 00:20:17,110
Okay.

521
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:19,220
I'll take a look now.

522
00:20:24,640 --> 00:20:25,440
Keep up.

523
00:20:27,310 --> 00:20:28,310
I think

524
00:20:28,850 --> 00:20:30,390
the site you chose is good,

525
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:31,940
but it's too secluded.

526
00:20:32,320 --> 00:20:33,180
We

527
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:36,120
