Consort Yue, your tongue

537
00:21:02,920 --> 00:21:04,540
is still as sharp as ever.

538
00:21:09,610 --> 00:21:11,760
Consort Yue, when will you

539
00:21:12,430 --> 00:21:13,980
remove this veil?

540
00:21:15,290 --> 00:21:16,720
When I fully recover,

541
00:21:16,740 --> 00:21:18,480
I will remove this veil.

542
00:21:19,310 --> 00:21:20,070
When?

543
00:21:20,390 --> 00:21:21,850
When the world is at peace.

544
00:21:24,630 --> 00:21:25,880
Just kidding.

545
00:21:26,440 --> 00:21:26,920
