546
00:21:27,720 --> 00:21:28,650
It won't be long.

547
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:29,550
Okay.

548
00:21:30,640 --> 00:21:31,640
I'll wait for you.

549
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:34,790
