569
00:22:11,960 --> 00:22:13,720
some reputable private shops.

570
00:22:13,880 --> 00:22:15,920
Over the past few days, I made a list,

571
00:22:17,160 --> 00:22:19,570
including restaurants,
taverns, and freight companies.

572
00:22:19,570 --> 00:22:21,490
I've personally investigated each of them.

573
00:22:21,490 --> 00:22:22,820
They are very reliable.

574
00:22:25,350 --> 00:22:26,890
Just by reading this list,

575
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:28,960
even the dumbest emperor

576
00:22:28,960 --> 00:22:30,310
would see that this consort

577
00:22:30,310 --> 00:22:30,660
is not suitable for important tasks.

578
00:22:30,660 --> 00:22:32,960
[Merchants for Rongying Academy]

579
00:22:32,960 --> 00:22:33,830
Every merchant on the list
belongs to the Yue family.

580
00:22:33,830 --> 00:22:35,960
[Yue's Ruiyunyun] [Yue's Fenghua House]
[Yue's Longpengsheng] [Yue's Jewelry Shop]

581
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:37,620
You're doing this on purpose?

582
00:22:37,750 --> 00:22:39,740
To make me believe you're selfish?

583
00:22:41,830 --> 00:22:42,440
Good.

584
00:22:43,200 --> 00:22:43,960
Very good.

585
00:22:45,160 --> 00:22:46,120
Good?

586
00:22:46,790 --> 00:22:48,400
I understand what you mean.

587
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:50,730
What do you understand?

588
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:56,060
You're concerned
in the early years of the dynasty,

589
00:22:56,220 --> 00:22:57,780
the treasury is still weak.

590
00:22:58,110 --> 00:22:58,920
So,

591
00:22:59,310 --> 00:23:01,970
you want to introduce
more private businesses.

592
00:23:02,200 --> 00:23:03,130
First,

593
00:23:03,510 --> 00:23:05,270
to boost the people's livelihood.

594
00:23:05,270 --> 00:23:05,880
Second,

595
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:07,830
to secure

596
00:23:08,030 --> 00:23:10,070
greater discounts for the court.

597
00:23:10,200 --> 00:23:11,160
Dog Huo,

598
00:23:11,620 --> 00:23:13,620
who said anything about discounts?

599
00:23:13,770 --> 00:23:15,560
Since these merchants

600
00:23:15,580 --> 00:23:16,830
are so enthusiastic

601
00:23:16,830 --> 00:23:18,340
about supporting the court's policy,

602
00:23:18,340 --> 00:23:20,680
I certainly can't be stingy.

603
00:23:21,320 --> 00:23:22,210
How about this?

604
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:23,850
I'll bestow upon them

605
00:23:23,920 --> 00:23:25,480
my own calligraphy

606
00:23:25,510 --> 00:23:27,110
to serve as their shop signs.

607
00:23:27,260 --> 00:23:28,260
What do you think?

608
00:23:28,650 --> 00:23:29,440
Wait.

609
00:23:33,360 --> 00:23:33,960
Come.

610
00:23:34,630 --> 00:23:35,320
Take a look.

611
00:23:38,180 --> 00:23:39,000
Hold this.

612
00:23:40,480 --> 00:23:41,480
What do you think?

613
00:23:42,300 --> 00:23:43,530
[Prosperous Shop]

614
00:23:43,530 --> 00:23:44,840
I missed a stroke here.

615
00:23:45,240 --> 00:23:46,580
But it doesn't matter.

616
00:23:46,680 --> 00:23:47,950
The handwriting...

617
00:23:48,470 --> 00:23:49,470
What about it?

618
00:23:50,360 --> 00:23:52,080
It's truly imperial in style.

619
00:23:52,440 --> 00:23:55,460
I spent much of my childhood
practicing martial arts.

620
00:23:56,190 --> 00:23:58,820
My calligraphy is rather poor.

621
00:23:59,330 --> 00:24:00,310
But...

622
00:24:00,440 --> 00:24:01,590
it's better than nothing.

623
00:24:01,590 --> 00:24:03,310
With my calligraphy

624
00:24:03,310 --> 00:24:05,240
as an embellishment,

625
00:24:05,790 --> 00:24:09,120
the merchants can consider it
fair trade for any discounts.

626
00:24:09,750 --> 00:24:12,560
Your Majesty, you're thoughtful.

627
00:24:13,590 --> 00:24:14,340
Here.

628
00:24:15,110 --> 00:24:15,910
Have some tea.

629
00:24:16,590 --> 00:24:17,240
Dog,

630
00:24:17,830 --> 00:24:19,670
since you're my future brother-in-law,

631
00:24:19,670 --> 00:24:21,330
I won't hold this against you.

632
00:24:21,910 --> 00:24:23,450
Once everything is settled,

633
00:24:23,450 --> 00:24:25,070
I'll leave.

634
00:24:34,820 --> 00:24:39,220
-Your Majesty, we wish you good health.
-Your Majesty, we wish you good health.

635
00:24:40,510 --> 00:24:41,240
Rise.

636
00:24:41,590 --> 00:24:42,990
Thank you, Your Majesty.

637
00:24:43,930 --> 00:24:46,610
This is your first time in the capital.

638
00:24:46,830 --> 00:24:48,350
I guess you've heard

639
00:24:48,760 --> 00:24:52,230
the system of hereditary peerage
has been abolished,

640
00:24:52,720 --> 00:24:55,240
replaced with a selection system.

641
00:24:57,460 --> 00:24:58,890
In my eyes,

642
00:24:59,190 --> 00:25:03,050
all of you are outstanding,

643
00:25:03,870 --> 00:25:05,660
worthy of a noble title.

644
00:25:07,110 --> 00:25:10,110
You will study in the Rongying Academy,

645
00:25:10,110 --> 00:25:11,970
awaiting the selection of heirs.

646
00:25:12,200 --> 00:25:13,310
His Majesty has already prepared

647
00:25:13,310 --> 00:25:14,960
fine lodgings and rare delicacies

648
00:25:14,960 --> 00:25:16,480
for you all.

649
00:25:16,640 --> 00:25:19,920
Each of you will have attendants
to see to your needs.

650
00:25:20,120 --> 00:25:22,270
The academy also has various shops.

651
00:25:22,310 --> 00:25:23,850
During your leisure time,

652
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:26,120
you'll have places for entertainment.

653
00:25:26,680 --> 00:25:27,400
Minister Du,

654
00:25:27,400 --> 00:25:28,380
introduce

655
00:25:28,720 --> 00:25:31,540
the academy's curriculums in detail.

656
00:25:32,720 --> 00:25:33,940
Your Majesty,

657
00:25:34,030 --> 00:25:36,540
customs vary widely across Ning.

658
00:25:36,750 --> 00:25:38,880
The curriculums have been designed to...

659
00:25:38,880 --> 00:25:40,620
It appears to be honor,

660
00:25:40,640 --> 00:25:42,430
but it's actually a gilded trap.

661
00:25:42,430 --> 00:25:43,720
Literary courses include zither, chess,
calligraphy, and painting.

662
00:25:43,720 --> 00:25:45,720
There must be someone capable behind this.

663
00:25:45,720 --> 00:25:47,050
The study of storybooks

664
00:25:47,160 --> 00:25:48,640
and appreciation of antiques.

665
00:25:48,640 --> 00:25:51,050
Martial courses include archery, polo,

666
00:25:51,200 --> 00:25:53,880
dance appreciation, beast dueling,
and games.

667
00:25:54,680 --> 00:25:56,030
So comprehensive.

668
00:25:59,110 --> 00:26:00,110
Your Highness.

669
00:26:00,310 --> 00:26:01,640
His Majesty came again.

670
00:26:02,160 --> 00:26:03,480
Again?

671
00:26:07,310 --> 00:26:08,640
Welcome, Your Majesty.

672
00:26:09,130 --> 00:26:09,930
You may leave.

673
00:26:10,400 --> 00:26:11,590
Yes, Your Majesty.

674
00:26:18,400 --> 00:26:19,200
Great.

675
00:26:20,200 --> 00:26:21,240
It's been so long

676
00:26:21,920 --> 00:26:23,640
since I felt this relaxed.

677
00:26:24,800 --> 00:26:27,600
The success of Rongying Academy—

678
00:26:28,070 --> 00:26:29,790
I owe it to you.

679
00:26:40,110 --> 00:26:40,640
Sit.

680
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:49,830
I can't remember

681
00:26:51,030 --> 00:26:52,600
the last time

682
00:26:52,830 --> 00:26:55,720
I drank freely like this.

683
00:26:58,510 --> 00:27:00,790
The dragon robe and crown

684
00:27:01,590 --> 00:27:02,400
feel like

685
00:27:03,310 --> 00:27:06,920
a skin that doesn't belong to me,

686
00:27:07,790 --> 00:27:09,720
wrapped so tightly around my body.

687
00:27:11,240 --> 00:27:13,240
Tonight, in front of you,

688
00:27:13,590 --> 00:27:15,920
I can shed it for a moment.

689
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:16,680
Come on.

690
00:27:18,830 --> 00:27:21,490
Let's drink
to our first victory in this battle.

691
00:27:30,830 --> 00:27:32,110
I never thought

692
00:27:33,680 --> 00:27:34,720
that one day,

693
00:27:35,180 --> 00:27:37,310
I would be drinking with you like this.

694
00:27:42,440 --> 00:27:43,680
Neither did I.

695
00:27:44,200 --> 00:27:46,200
Who would've thought the red thread

696
00:27:46,440 --> 00:27:48,590
of the God of Matchmaking
would tie you and Ling'er together?

697
00:27:48,590 --> 00:27:49,880
And now I have to work hard

698
00:27:49,880 --> 00:27:51,680
to handle court affairs for you.

699
00:27:52,790 --> 00:27:53,480
Tell me,

700
00:27:55,110 --> 00:27:56,350
if two years ago,

701
00:27:57,680 --> 00:27:59,340
I hadn't ascended the throne,

702
00:28:00,510 --> 00:28:01,910
what would it be like now?

703
00:28:05,260 --> 00:28:07,190
You speak as if you never wanted it.

704
00:28:08,000 --> 00:28:09,680
Actually, I didn't.

705
00:28:10,310 --> 00:28:13,480
Back then, all I wanted
was to roam the world with a sword.

706
00:28:18,350 --> 00:28:20,420
That sounds like you're showing off.

707
00:28:20,890 --> 00:28:22,800
If you didn't want to be the emperor,

708
00:28:22,800 --> 00:28:24,860
where did this dragon robe come from?

709
00:28:25,550 --> 00:28:26,520
At that time,

710
00:28:27,640 --> 00:28:29,440
the capital had already fallen.

711
00:28:29,750 --> 00:28:30,810
The Volunteer Army

712
00:28:31,260 --> 00:28:33,500
turned against each other over who

713
00:28:33,680 --> 00:28:35,140
should ascend the throne.

714
00:28:35,510 --> 00:28:37,240
No one could reach a consensus.

715
00:28:37,680 --> 00:28:38,510
In the end,

716
00:28:38,720 --> 00:28:41,310
they pushed me,
someone from the martial arts world,

717
00:28:41,310 --> 00:28:42,790
onto the throne.

718
00:28:44,830 --> 00:28:46,330
If you really didn't want it,

719
00:28:46,330 --> 00:28:48,130
you could have just walked away.

720
00:28:48,310 --> 00:28:49,170
But you didn't.

721
00:28:50,070 --> 00:28:51,120
So deep down,

722
00:28:52,110 --> 00:28:53,350
you did want it.

723
00:28:56,050 --> 00:28:58,570
I fought my way here

724
00:28:59,750 --> 00:29:01,350
only because I wanted

725
00:29:01,750 --> 00:29:03,240
the war to end.

726
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:12,680
On my way to the capital,

727
00:29:13,260 --> 00:29:15,520
I saw too many faces that looked the same—

728
00:29:16,150 --> 00:29:17,880
faces without light

729
00:29:18,720 --> 00:29:19,790
or hope.

730
00:29:20,590 --> 00:29:22,050
They lived precariously.

731
00:29:23,270 --> 00:29:25,820
One moment they might find
half a loaf of bread,

732
00:29:25,820 --> 00:29:28,780
but the next—a blade through the belly.

733
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:31,800
But life shouldn't be like that.

734
00:29:45,880 --> 00:29:46,680
Don't hit me.

735
00:29:46,680 --> 00:29:47,750
Please.

736
00:29:49,310 --> 00:29:50,240
Don't be afraid.

737
00:29:51,110 --> 00:29:52,310
Where is your family?

738
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:54,270
They're gone.

739
00:29:55,830 --> 00:29:57,030
I'll take you home.

740
00:29:57,050 --> 00:29:58,830
You're not here to kill me?

741
00:30:01,800 --> 00:30:02,680
Don't worry.

742
00:30:03,620 --> 00:30:05,710
I will keep you safe.

743
00:30:06,900 --> 00:30:09,500
I wish children could
get the chance to grow up,

744
00:30:09,740 --> 00:30:12,830
and the elderly could
spend their final days at home.

745
00:30:13,070 --> 00:30:15,930
Isn't that how life should be—
simple and ordinary?

746
00:30:16,730 --> 00:30:17,740
If I left,

747
00:30:18,400 --> 00:30:20,530
the Volunteer Army would split again,

748
00:30:20,540 --> 00:30:22,520
and countless lives would be lost.

749
00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:27,110
In this capital,

750
00:30:28,290 --> 00:30:30,630
there are many hidden monsters.

751
00:30:31,650 --> 00:30:33,290
Did you know what you'd

752
00:30:35,030 --> 00:30:37,240
have to give up for the throne?

753
00:30:37,330 --> 00:30:38,040
I did.

754
00:30:40,700 --> 00:30:41,880
My freedom,

755
00:30:43,040 --> 00:30:44,450
my happiness,

756
00:30:46,270 --> 00:30:48,740
and the most genuine

757
00:30:49,630 --> 00:30:52,140
and important part of myself.

758
00:30:53,490 --> 00:30:54,550
I'd be trapped here

759
00:30:55,550 --> 00:30:56,920
for the rest of my life.

760
00:30:57,220 --> 00:30:58,170
I'd battle with

761
00:30:58,770 --> 00:31:01,570
countless schemes and intrigues forever.

762
00:31:03,070 --> 00:31:04,720
But someone once told me—

763
00:31:06,830 --> 00:31:08,690
for the sake of a beautiful world,

764
00:31:09,730 --> 00:31:11,600
for the peace of the people,

765
00:31:13,350 --> 00:31:13,790
bear

766
00:31:14,740 --> 00:31:16,350
the burden of the court,

767
00:31:21,680 --> 00:31:23,880
and face every problem without regret.

768
00:31:31,590 --> 00:31:32,620
Is it worth it?

769
00:31:34,720 --> 00:31:35,440
Yes.

770
00:31:49,620 --> 00:31:50,880
Is there any wine left?

771
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:55,090
Are you alright?

772
00:31:55,270 --> 00:31:57,130
Has it triggered your old injury?

773
00:31:57,380 --> 00:31:59,980
How does he know
about my old injury on my chest?

774
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:03,090
Does he know who I am?

775
00:32:03,110 --> 00:32:03,750
Here.

776
00:32:04,320 --> 00:32:05,070
Be careful.

777
00:32:08,090 --> 00:32:11,590
What old injury? You must be mistaken.

778
00:32:14,060 --> 00:32:15,150
Yue Chi.

779
00:32:20,110 --> 00:32:21,200
Consort Yue.

780
00:32:22,590 --> 00:32:24,070
I remember now.

781
00:32:24,750 --> 00:32:26,440
Yue Chi is already dead.

782
00:32:29,720 --> 00:32:31,000
I shot

783
00:32:32,980 --> 00:32:34,620
that arrow myself.

784
00:32:35,350 --> 00:32:36,750
At Dayan Pass.

785
00:32:38,810 --> 00:32:39,920
But I missed.

786
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:41,260
Sit.

787
00:32:47,180 --> 00:32:48,630
Your archery skills

788
00:32:48,840 --> 00:32:50,770
aren't that impressive after all.

789
00:32:55,040 --> 00:32:57,120
I did it on purpose.

790
00:33:00,670 --> 00:33:01,430
Why?

791
00:33:02,320 --> 00:33:03,800
I valued his talent.

792
00:33:04,440 --> 00:33:06,390
I couldn't bear to see him die.

793
00:33:08,540 --> 00:33:09,720
I didn't expect

794
00:33:10,110 --> 00:33:11,940
that he was so frail.

795
00:33:13,720 --> 00:33:16,400
I deliberately aimed
away from his vital parts

796
00:33:16,430 --> 00:33:18,740
and used only 30% of my strength,

797
00:33:19,800 --> 00:33:21,310
yet he still died.

798
00:33:22,270 --> 00:33:23,640
Too fragile.

799
00:33:23,660 --> 00:33:24,660
I'm not...

800
00:33:25,500 --> 00:33:26,430
Not what?

801
00:33:31,880 --> 00:33:33,030
You're drunk.

802
00:33:33,480 --> 00:33:34,810
You must have misheard.

803
00:33:35,790 --> 00:33:37,890
Who do you think you're looking down on?

804
00:33:37,890 --> 00:33:38,780
So...

805
00:33:38,820 --> 00:33:40,080
that's what happened.

806
00:33:40,430 --> 00:33:41,970
Back then on the battlefield,

807
00:33:41,970 --> 00:33:43,730
I tricked him quite a few times.

808
00:33:43,970 --> 00:33:46,370
But in the end, he was the one
who let me live.

809
00:33:47,240 --> 00:33:49,000
I do owe him a favor.

810
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:51,160
Consort Yue,

811
00:33:51,950 --> 00:33:53,010
actually,

812
00:33:54,600 --> 00:33:56,340
I did it for you too.

813
00:33:59,550 --> 00:34:00,790
God, not now. Say whatever you want

814
00:34:00,790 --> 00:34:02,590
after Ling'er and I switch back.

815
00:34:02,610 --> 00:34:06,020
For your sake,

816
00:34:06,410 --> 00:34:08,429
I can accept

817
00:34:08,889 --> 00:34:10,580
everything around you,

818
00:34:10,730 --> 00:34:12,199
including your brother.

819
00:34:12,659 --> 00:34:15,040
If you know where he is,

820
00:34:15,320 --> 00:34:16,960
tell him to show up openly.

821
00:34:17,650 --> 00:34:18,500
I promise

822
00:34:19,120 --> 00:34:20,770
I will keep him safe.

823
00:34:21,270 --> 00:34:23,710
My previous promise remains unchanged.

824
00:34:24,360 --> 00:34:27,060
He can still
be the prime minister of Ning,

825
00:34:27,080 --> 00:34:28,610
fulfilling his ambitions.

826
00:34:31,540 --> 00:34:33,420
When I reorganize Ning,

827
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:36,929
I'll still appoint you
as the prime minister!

828
00:34:36,969 --> 00:34:38,480
That's just drunk talk.

829
00:34:38,920 --> 00:34:40,260
I'm the former prime minister
from the last dynasty.

830
00:34:40,260 --> 00:34:41,900
If I serve you in your dynasty,

831
00:34:41,900 --> 00:34:43,429
I'd be a walking target.

832
00:34:43,449 --> 00:34:45,600
I have no interest in seeking death.

833
00:34:45,920 --> 00:34:46,960
What did you say?

834
00:34:50,070 --> 00:34:50,969
I...

835
00:34:51,550 --> 00:34:52,630
am deeply moved.

836
00:34:52,929 --> 00:34:54,860
I thank you on behalf of my brother.

837
00:34:58,400 --> 00:35:00,750
Tonight's wine is far too strong.

838
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:02,890
I'll ask someone here to serve you.

839
00:35:07,650 --> 00:35:08,510
I can't stay here with him

840
00:35:08,510 --> 00:35:09,710
like this any longer.

841
00:35:10,030 --> 00:35:12,070
Ling'er and I must switch back
as soon as possible.

842
00:35:12,070 --> 00:35:12,840
But...

843
00:35:13,360 --> 00:35:15,160
I should ask Ling'er first.
